	(24, 1, 'c hnh Bun Ma Thut | Ngy 1 | TPHCM - Bun Ma Thut, 500Km vt o', 'Ngy u tin trong chuyn i Bun Ma Thut. Vi hnh trnh gn 500km.', '<p><strong>Ngy u tin trong chuyn i Bun Ma Thut di ba ngy hai m.</strong></p><p><strong>Track map qung ng t TP.HCM n Bun Ma Thut ti </strong><a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=1pESrFguDvns1kpccLKVB08x3mzG5EQDU&amp;usp=sharing"><strong>y</strong></a><strong>.</strong></p><p>Xin cho mi ngi, mnh l Qung Dng. Mnh va thc hin xong chuyn i Bun Ma Thut vo dp Tt canh T 2020  nh du mt nm y th thch vi mnh, mnh c nhiu d nh, k hoch phi thc hin trong nm nay. y cng l chuyn i c hnh u tin mnh chy ln Ty Nguyn, v cng s l pht sng u cho hnh trnh khm ph Ty Nguyn ca mnh sau ny, :v.</p><p>Lan man qu, vo thng vn  lun, h h.</p><p>Ni thm v qu trnh mnh quyt nh v ln k hoch cho chuyn i. Lc u, mnh nh l s chinh phc cung ng ven bin n vi thnh ph Quy Nhn (Bnh nh) y nng v gi, ti mnh cng thch bin. Nhng li thay i v li ha vi mt ngi - ng ln Bun Ma Thut i, ri tui dn ng thm qu ca tui - v mnh quyt nh bo ln Bun Ma Thut.</p><p>Mnh ln k hoch m v track map trong mt ngy. Thng thng, nu i Bun Ma Thut (vit tt - BMT) th mi ngi u ngh i QL14 - con ng huyn thoi xuyn Ty Nguyn. Nhng mnh th khc, mnh chn cung ng theo QL20 n Madagui, r vo DT721 n th trn  Th, ri vt o Lc Bc n ng ba Lc Bo, tip tc theo QL28 n Gia Ngha, ri t Gia Ngha n Nam Kar theo ng DT684, nhp vo QL27  n BMT. Cung ny th di hn QL14 khong 120Km, nhng i qua nhiu a danh hn, ng cng vng xe, cnh rt p, c bit l rt t trm xx (h h).</p><p><strong>Chi tit :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Mnh xut pht t nh  Bnh Tn lc 2h sng, thng tin qua Xa L H Ni ri n ng ba Du Giy. on ny cng khng c g ng ni, mt phn do mnh i ti, phn th nhiu anh em cng qu rnh on ny ri. Ch c iu l i sm, sng m kh dy, lnh, mnh phi mc hai lp o mi cm thy n (do mnh cha tng i tour trong iu kin nh ny).</p><p>4h sng, mnh ngh mt cht ti cy xng ngay ng ba Du Giy. Sau  tip tc hnh trnh theo QL20 n ng ba DT721. T Du Giy n DT721 khong 80Km, mnh chy tm 1h20 pht th n.</p><p>5h20 sng, mnh r tri vo DT721, thng tin n  Th. Lc ny tri vn cn kh ti, on ng ny li khng h c n ng nn mnh chy chm.</p><p>5h40 sng, mnh va n cu  Huoai th tri cng hng sng. Bnh mnh cao nguyn tht p, khng kh trong lnh, cng thm ci se lnh ca vng cao na. Mnh dng li chp tm hnh ri i tip.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-32zKqQ9QLXVViXp9lyLL2l0eS4dGV9njLjcJYxPvLs2MQr-P06BwVkCHVYaFvt9VPMPC1UKzBuMFh0zFWX0TQHJwVmphU3XcWwiPZabDHHn7fK1v7hjFSoJ5uhbk7oEKLtDVjRqeA=w2044-h1532-no"><figcaption>Dng  Huoai trong bui bnh minh.</figcaption></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-kf3O71_EHiaflfPiMzKV8fQHJKmURhRnXbPb6lNyOmZQ0MmWCJfFnpMH2bbGElWmUVJAfdXSG7BRCh1pphaByw7zD_PwU_ccka8APO81yZx0Urgkwt1MLxMQBi03iaIy5_BZ4wfxw=w2044-h1532-no"><figcaption>Bnh minh ni cao nguyn.</figcaption></figure><p>6h10, mnh n th trn  Th. Khng bit l do mnh i vo dp Tt hay sao m ni y bnh yn n l. Yn tnh, trong lnh. Rt t ngi dn ra ng. C l l do cn kh sm.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/KW8CSS97ESrxhs-Sjp5jP6SK7cab7GF4pO8qBv9G7Ovv9hB3lTnHM1a7UZGmw9rKoxe4Tc_1xuxNwMqlQmNJ5gwHs6is0dLW-4BX5JGThV-9VOcNnzcym-f4W5i9TKjryxOOfoVvlw=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption>Ngh t thi, i ri.</figcaption></figure><p>6h30, sau khi n sng nh vi bnh m ngt v mt ngm tr gng nng mang theo, mnh tip tc hnh trnh. Ra khi  Th, mnh r vo DT725, thng tin n o Lc Bc.</p><p>6h50, mnh bt u leo o Lc Bc, o Lc Bc l mt con o kh di, nm trn ng DT725 ni  Th n Bo Lc (Lm ng). y cng l mt cch i  Lt cho bn no khng thch QL20 quen thuc, mun khm ph mt cung ng mi.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/vNDgZ52wmh36vpHy5vWLJ3EP524GYM3e762mqKPniJe8sT5XOZrefkJKlnurKT8pClpmnJRE_3ZVA9FlEdm3MleY8KLSz00HDViZOVBjK0kZHUgU2-Z3D8nKMDPAGp3Y1I6zThyLvQ=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption>Vt o Lc Bc thi.</figcaption></figure><p>o kh vng, rt t ngi qua li, cnh hai bn th khng phi bn, p tuyt vi. n y, mnh cm thy rt thoi mi, mi u phin u c vt b. Khng kh mt m, ting chim ht, cn trng ku, khung cnh thin nhin hng v, tt c to nn mt tri nghim m mnh khng th no qun c.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/bEONI3WlRKHJJRHNJu531JqZe80rvVSdQfgyjha-E1tIkCLyt5lp3REc5sFfFfd1TPWotV3JQVBmHgfJU4PktVePMsEcUZsVXiq-qOl60cZj0jaVnxJ72YfEvWgrFs-CZhLNEVuhug=w862-h1532-no"><figcaption>Lc Bc hng v.</figcaption></figure><p>7h10, mnh ti nh o Lc Bc. Thi tit cn kh lnh. Mnh c check ng h Casio th l 18  C.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/RJU5AsozCiqnNEIfVRyx2GaEFdqgK6C5UcDea-f8nZTNT4WGo9RlTRCB1ZXfjVYr6V4s6MPv-Hm8nK8cHID2wbNpHJOGFx5t628VdHB0ClYbwilkWMk5W4QyB2Uhghq1J4ZSDfLiPA=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption>Thung lng my nhn t nh o Lc Bc.</figcaption></figure><p>7h20, in thoi mt sng, GPS cng khng c, :(. Mnh dng li mt cht, kim tra xe c, hnh l xem cn chc chn khng, chp vi tm hnh, hp vi ngm tr cho m bng ri i tip.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/6xWuVPUzSKD1RiLDbmtuEC7EDuIRzsueNCOuyA5czpdsUs656PUdpFbmu0gllBEH-tRt_62Ujq1RO6hoofYfM8toxy1TRLnz7wygABSVDgvWrsMyVavzgmUzFwGUzwrRNCkKmLbmVg=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption> o Lc Bc.</figcaption></figure><p>Phi ni Lc Bc qu l con o p, nhng cng hi s. Hn 7h sng nhng ni y kh m u, c l l trin o bn ny khng c mt tri chiu. GPS thng xuyn mt tn hiu, c nhng on mt tri khng chiu ti th sng dy, rt lnh, mnh phi m mm trong bin sng, va chy va bp kn  gy ch . Mnh khng dm dng li, do o vng, quanh co, dc cao nn nguy him. M ni tht, mnh nghe kh nhiu chuyn tm linh v con o ny, cng n n, :)).</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/jr1InY108W81_fs-vvlxEbBPGnEy00pP-xJylGEWBOkP9t0QPWIT2AefbZmEkd-JxtosL30deYf6TuJ0JEHUqlteCwecdlXfA46s7LCRppwCky4bImbgN0vDCapZyt09Nm7EI3lFiA=w862-h1532-no"><figcaption>m u o Lc Bc.</figcaption></figure><p>Sau gn 40 pht ng o, 8h th mnh ti ng ba Lc Bo. Dng ngh, ung ngm tr, kim tra xe c mt ln na ri i tip.</p><p>n ng ba Lc Bo, mnh r tri theo QL28 i k Glong. QL28 on ny th kh n, ng tng i tt, hai bn nh ca tha tht, xen k vi my ry c ph ang ra hoa, thm lng. C mt s on sng m dy, lnh ct da. Mnh ngc nhin l  hn 8h m sng vn kh dy (c l do y l ln u mnh ln cao nguyn nn mnh thy l :)) ).</p><p>9h, sau mt gi ng h va chy va ngm cnh, mnh  ti ng ba vo thu in ng Nai 4</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/WMHPnRLXMVZmDooVMY_nNffawiMAqJijSAMEfReBYlbTXv2lAnHiECx3ew7odpFHWjmOTujxizVdz2CiMkAiaRrUFL-uB_uUh47OOEgcHzA8C4Z_ZDVsFBa-arWXT3J5FRJHx0u4YA=w862-h1532-no"><figcaption>Thu in ng nai 4 sng sng gia ni rng.</figcaption></figure><p>9h20, mnh n ng ba Qung Kh (im nhp ca 2 ng QL28 - bn xem bn  s r). Dng xe, check bn , kim tra xe, n bnh v ung tr, lm vi ng Thn Quyn mn m mnh hc qua Tin tri d tr Trn Tiger (:v) cho kho ngi. Ti y l mnh  i c hn na ng, cn khong 220Km na l n ngay nh ngh.</p><p>Do cn sm, nn mnh quyt nh chy ln h T ng (ng i h T ng ngc li vi hng mnh nh i).</p><p>9h40, do ng kh xu nn mnh quyt nh quay li, vi cng tranh th chy ti ni sm  lm th tc check-in phng.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/E-lGvRUmmXeauwgk9KdTDM3En5x5pndf4SUbcR_JFkBRM42UzPjm09WK5z88kuLjkvgiu6xrFpzflsSFJj58Yz4eXfxX_EVt15XndfyKiXCdtmlq7_6cMvcJ5QzpI_1dNaC06YKrqQ=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption>H T ng (gc ny khng thy c s hng v ca h, nu mun thy h r hn, cc bn nn chy tip khong 30Km na)</figcaption></figure><p>10h10, mnh n TP.Gia Ngha, t Gia Ngha, mnh r phi vo ng DT684.  y, nu bn no cm thy ui th c th i thng theo QL28  ra li QL14, ri theo QL14 i BMT (t giao l QL28 - QL14 n BMT khong 120Km)</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/IBwt3699UClAiIt7NX58L47ZvKVwupOnBpLnWLQ0eYk-sY6Qi8uLRDeKs0Z__6kBIImQBNc-OiuJloqXkhpNBLvpYx5GGwHeTM43uPEEWmv-jJrokmfpGKNkI5gePOKJT8Dm8d1gCA=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption>Thnh ph Gia Ngha.</figcaption></figure><p>Mnh men theo DT684 v pha Nam Kar. ng DT864 kh tt, dng nh n va c ci to, mnh thy lp nha ng cn kh mi. Cnh 2 bn th cng khng ni bt, ch l bt ngn ry c ph. Thi tit cng khng cn lnh na, do cng hn 10h ri, nhng cng khng qu l nng, ni chung l thoi mi.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/Mj52nyIs4Qf5HAnFve7P7ZEPKPIZJEmOYIZRSZ203dsiUm5FghGrWPR6W0tp1_ajghaXs8Ve6P2ES0UGDsaZHaphqaXHckAh_kvMaB9LqDUDnDhroRxNupF4ILCGIEWtdEfo6_-I9Q=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption>Vy l em Ch*h x (Gixxer) ny cng i vi mnh c 8000Km ri. Cm n em.</figcaption></figure><p>11h15, sau hn 45Km, mnh bt u i vo ng rng. Mnh check bn  th thy y l mt phn ca rng Nam Nung (khu bo tn thin nhin Nam Nung). Hai bn cy rng cao ln, khng kh trong lnh, mt m, mnh dng li ngh chn, u phi lc no cng c c hi thng thc khng gian gia rng gi Ty Nguyn u.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/66W0TmaKU8hgMNcTFYZ3wI0NhiOLPxsEvvgQwsXx6tJLHurHpkCfFnCSEYjESuYi-vdbazqiYLJcK2H5ttFSyHr3oPDCeaDXLWllK8iAw1vaFGCSa-PCNksNPo0NuVshkJaEQQYXNw=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption>Con ng xuyn rng Nam Nung.</figcaption></figure><p>11h45, mnh n ng ba vo thu in Bun Tua Srah. Mnh r phi vo mt con ng m google khng bit tn. ng ny l ng b tng, t , hai bn l cy tiu th phi, mnh khng chc lm.</p><p>12h, mnh ti cu Nam Kar. Ngh mt cht, kim tra cc th. Thi tit bt u kh nng, tuy khng bng di ng bng.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/W62DtGGQCfNV5HXIyzbsKzlhTEXSD70NlPACJ1SJqsfbuiV_NHSPnO4c8xvK8S-UnEGhHHKjiAk-dJ_S0dC_zrMrGDdbm-ctYqswLhz2SODgiJYFCOsTPvZLaMFf-bJI_U-ZQKNHTA=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption>Dng Krng N xanh thm.</figcaption></figure><p>12h10, mnh ti p thu in Bun Tua Srah. Cn c mng bt u. on ng t p Bun Tua Srah n QL27 cc k xu.  g,  voi lin tc, bi m mt, t  kh. cng may l mnh i vo ma kh, ch ma ma l thua. c ci cnh quan kh p, mt bn l ba rng, mt bn l h Bun Tua Srah rng ln.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/Hd2GOt0BmSFQj2KBveEKd9d8R3IGLI8k0OS0xHyHqLTlCAzu8dJzeNz48KtYBsBjb4PWLIMyuLa4bLsA6CZcfRFDJz_gYpPGPOz_vZFFq03QiIQqkOYSWd7CYZz4zFrjB7kOBEaspw=w2044-h1532-no"><figcaption>Dng chn ct li hnh l cho chc n. Pha xa kia l h Bun Tua Srah.</figcaption></figure><p>13h30, mnh ti a phn huyn Lk sau gn 30km vt o theo QL27. Do cng tra nn mnh khng dng  chp hnh nhiu. QL27 on t Nam Kar i Lk kh ep, ng tt nhng cng nhiu cua tay o, dc cao trn 10 , l mt th thch cho cc tay ni mi.</p><p>Ti huyn Lk, mnh quyt nh vt sng Krng Ana bng cch bng qua  Bun M`Ling. Ti y nhiu bn chc hn s thc mc, mnh s gii thch lun l mnh s n nh mt ngi rt quan trng trc ri mi n BMT. Cc bn c th t Lk i BMT bng QL27, ng t y cng d i hn ri, h h.</p><p>Nu cc bn vn cn hng th vi hnh trnh n BMT ca mnh th xin mi cc bn c tip.</p><p>13h50, mnh n a phn huyn Krng Ana sau khi vt sng. Con ng pha trc n mnh bng t  cao nguyn, bng nhng ry c ph trng hoa thm lng.</p><p>14h30, mnh n x Qung in, do bn mnh  gn y, tic l c y bn vic nh t xut nn khng tip mnh c :(, bun lm lun, c y l mt trong nhng l do mnh i BMT m, hiu hiu.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/vSRYIEV5seXy4mBI46ZnxHahAjgzsUjo4vmEu-hzQCf4PdHYTlZJ5jBW_58v9fJ1Jvel-_T79VkHRQB3GZ-dokID6IdQSAnTcn85VzX8_X2RF0qqLOMZs-NuEHxT9UR9hcy3o-hfhw=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption>UBND x Qung in.</figcaption></figure><p>15h30, mnh  n nh ngh, kt thc qung ng 480Km t TP.HCM n TP.BMT.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/_WR314sEHRMQpCA9aZIyKse65wo9grSvFWl4UChtZ00_DVfdPmjSOJUurGsZQmRomT2xowEAFlVPZMmU_vIwHFTDBKQHGHftmM_PaB6fR2822m0IAHCMqVjJrhnWA4yqLHOeUcGW5g=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption>Nh ngh Ngc Trn - ng Y Wang, TP.BMT</figcaption></figure><p>18h, sau gn hn 2 gi nh gic, mnh quyt nh i n, i qu ri. M cng nhn, khng kh cao nguyn lm cho mnh ng kh ngon, hi hi. Mnh chn mn bnh canh c dm kh ni ting  BMT. Qun bnh canh Hng &nbsp;- 57 Hai B Trng, Thng Li, BMT, k Lk c bn mnh khuyn nn th. OK, duyt!</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/mP3mPXJHuNceR60MCP6s1p6SDNkPP0reFcVfG5FYXJm_eTx8QbB88WQcG4iAoP1V_wBYc-mWq55qQIm5VNLQKGGU5bVzEoLsQ5KTB8lyyfDwuGfzMVtmyNaKN_U6GrHxWrcZDQITNg=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption>Phn nh vy l 30k, kh kinh t.</figcaption></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/njDdL0OTDoyACH6vCJfBrndr