ong iu kin thi tit nh th ny.</p><p>7h30, sau khong 10 pht dng i, mnh quyt nh i tip, do c vic cn v gii quyt. Mnh chn chc chy chm, tp trung quan st.</p><p>8h30, mnh ra khi a phn k Mil, lc ny th tri cng tan sng mt phn. Mnh cng chy xe t tin hn mt t. Tuy nhin, vn cn phi cn thn, do c im ca QL14 l my anh xx, an ton l trn ht m, h h.</p><p>9h20, mnh n thnh ph Gia Ngha. Dng xe kim tra li mi th, n nh phn xi mua lc chy qua k Mil. y, hi mt phn sc.</p><p>12h00, mnh n thnh ph ng Xoi thuc tnh Bnh Phc, do mnh tranh th chy nn cng khng c chp chot g nhiu.</p><p>14h10, mnh n cu vt Sng Thn, vo a phn thnh ph HCM.</p><p>14h47, mnh ti nh, kt thc chuyn i c hnh thnh ph HCM - thnh ph Bun Ma Thut.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/Zsk-VQzZdCc7rd2xUMEVFzs-iaT8ednuQN_6wKpLWwmdntEoseUITSfAcNI9M45FuIeN0IxpP5DGD8wWiGxYocX3bEe8opps_beGBwqeQYrT8zCUpNuZMc-Hd0g0oSHku7qjGrNuui1Zbnxbu1D7bDkgawpKMlvagqJXses-keoKIev4Xotvy6EXMNGSpTaim8yT9ZLBHp_OSZvjFd8aMZlAOaNaD4DAZ5UO7IX2y5cfy3xV8f1XbNj6BJaJDIbz0n1mpOLFeG_hHoH50Bj_A5HTqsAeyB_YHpLbVtW_2zH_eeoNjz13TlrRRQKxSBbZNq4HDt41o3jobAI9b6DlkQFGeqfvD4-eDORJ8P04-Vd_2weiTsj8WmWWn2V4sKleDdWH197GtJWBfige_D5J_At-3F9tM8izll41RZQA-vebFvgoVF_J8590NnsrTLILviJKerPlKQNVEKZ5Nkjb_Bl5_VdUgNUri7brjwmX4CCy8P5xFWDgytEGNrJMSZlHMNoSyUbA7tUQLYSbqHV4FEn1sp4KyKkWc3D4lhJ71aWRQNCX7MkLjMFfyn9iDRHhlFqMa1WOglAUOkRWo_Qnw4ptRhCGgd09-TocyMGQi-YNOEPskkLidQxkhRhU7KKKnFB70Y29M3PIAE7WgGBAq-8zwvn_kMdZdNEKKjJzZ09Mll2qN9doKwHeJJz5gH5qaB-3F0OC18ccWIAjIOUhoM5VT32_z2E34jVPQnG_ksd4wqfNndppaQ=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption>Ti nh ri, dui nh tri chui.</figcaption></figure><p>Chi ph ngy cui:&nbsp;</p><p>- Nh ngh 2 m : 350k</p><p>- Xng : 100k</p><p>Tng: 450k</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Tng kt chuyn i:</strong></p><p>Phi ni y l cung mang li rt nhiu tri nghim cho mnh.</p><p>Mnh khng chn l trnh m nhiu ngi vn chn l QL14 t Bnh Phc i, mnh chn cung t Du Giy -  Th - k Glong - Gia Ngha - Nam Kar - Lk - Bun Ma Thut.</p><p>Cung ny c qung ng khong 480Km, l trnh i qua o Lc Bc, mt con o rt rt rt p, qua thu in ng Nai 4, thu in Bun Tua Srah hng v. Cng kh l gan khi quyt nh chn l trnh ny, do l trnh ny khng c nhiu ngi i qua nn kh t review, i vi tm trng nm np khng bit l ng i c tt khng, cnh c p khng, v tht khng tht vng, cht lng ng cc tt, cnh 2 bn ng cc p, khi th len li gia nhng ry c ph thm lng, khi th chnh vnh bn vc, bn vch.</p><p>Ni v o Lc Bc. y l con o him tr nht mnh tng i, s s c 8 khc cua tay o trn gn 20Km ng o, cnh hai bn rt p, c nhiu on sng m rt dy v c mt s on GPS khng xc nh c (lc ny s vi).</p><p>on DT684 t Gia Ngha n Nam Kar cng l mt con ng rt tuyt vi, rng cy thng xanh c, rng thng rng l c, cht lng mt ng kh tt, ng mi c trng li nha.</p><p>on ng t DT684 n QL27 qua rng Nam Kar (mnh cng khng bit ng ny tn g, google map khng c thng tin :v ), c khong 12Km off-road (sport-bike m off-road th khoai thi ri) ng kh xu (on t p thu in Bun Tua Srah n QL27), c ci l thy c p thu in rt hng v, h Bun Tua Srah nc xanh ngc, cc p, on ny l on bo sc ca mnh kh l nhiu.</p><p>on QL27 n TP.Bun Ma Thut, y l ng quc l nn cht lng ng cng rt tt, cnh cng p, nhiu cua tay o vi  dc kh cao.</p><p>V th mnh chn cung QL14 cho nhn, cng ti lc i lm mu, la ng xa, kh  i. M cung ny th nhiu ngi review ri, ni chung QL14 p. , mnh v lc 6h sng th c mt cht bn tc khi va ra khi TP.Bun Ma Thut. My anh lm vic sing nng gh :v.</p><p>Tm li, chuyn i ny  li cho mnh nhiu tri nghim nh l chy xe gia sng m di tri ti en lc 4h sng trn QL20; mt mnh gia o trong mn sng m dy c vi in thoi b mt GPS cng ci lnh 16  C; b vi vn tc di 30Km trn QL14 v cht;...</p><p>Tng qung ng c i v v: 998,3Km.</p><p>Tng chi ph: 1008k cho mt chuyn i 3 ngy 2 m.</p><p>Track map xem ti <a href=" https://drive.google.com/open?id=1pESrFguDvns1kpccLKVB08x3mzG5EQDU&amp;usp=sharing">y</a>.</p><p>Cc bn c th xem chi tit hnh trnh qua knh Youtube ca mnh ti <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B2fp8XlIULg&amp;list=PLheZEJ9DRtXlpncHF8oaEPu5xmeN_QUnY&amp;index=12">y</a>.</p><p><strong>Vy l hnh trnh c hnh ca mnh cng kt thc tt p, cng c mt cht nui tic, khng gp c ngi mun gp, khng n c mt s ni mnh mun n. Nhng khng sao, vn cn nhiu dp, mnh s quay li chinh phc, khng phi ch Bun Ma Thut m l c Ty Nguyn. Cm cc bn  theo di hnh trnh ca mnh. Hn gp cc bn trong nhng bi vit tip theo.</strong></p><p><strong>Chc cc bn s c nhng chuyn i an ton v vui v.</strong></p><p><i><strong>"Four wheels move the body, but two wheels move the soul".</strong></i></p><p><i>Xem thm: </i><a href="https://dunglu.herokuapp.com/#/blogs/album/49">Cung c hnh TPHCM - Phan Rang - Thp Chm | 11/2019.</a></p>', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/tTQW25lFoFQ1esOS8vYI7LHWjP3QRSOgBiL0u21Bp-TRhQFNXQCrTyaA1rJ9BhZtIMmaWBJcRG4muI9XYKXfK4X8DnhMEsxQ1rPN0kDtdKpH7D-FGYtwodLgPKuzw_a0Pp4Zblssaw=w1150-h1532-no', 1586525907, 1, 1587610865, 1, 1, 0),
	(27, 49, 'c hnh Phan Rang - Thp Chm | Ngy 1 | Hnh trnh 410Km n vi x ''Nng nh Phan, gi nh Rang''', 'Hnh trnh vt 410Km dc theo cung ng ven bin n vi thnh ph Phan Rang - Thp chm.', '<p><strong>Xin cho cc bn, vo ngy 15/11/2019, mnh c lm mt chuyn c hnh dc theo ng ven bin n vi thnh ph Phan Rang - Thp Chm (vit tt Phan Rang).</strong></p><p><strong>Bn  chi tit cc bn c th xem ti </strong><a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=1LkLDla8oEyhsosQdkKyn5HhEgNcZZqgk&amp;usp=sharing"><strong>y</strong></a><strong>.</strong></p><p>y l chuyn i trn 1000Km u tin m mnh i c hnh cng GSXR150. V hnh trnh ln ny, mnh chn cung ven bin t thnh ph bin Vng Tu, men theo QL55 n rng Bnh Chu - Phc Bu, xuyn rng n H Cc, ri theo QL55 n La Gi, qua K G, n thnh ph Phan Thit, ri t Phan Thit, i Hn Rm, Mi N, vt Bu Trng - Phan R Ca huyn thoi, n Tuy Phong, men theo bin C N vo Phc Dim, ri th tri trn o Khng Hi n Mi Dinh, cui cng l vt cu An ng  n Phan Rang. L trnh ny s xa hn i QL1A quen thuc, nhng vng xe hn, cnh cng p hn.</p><p><strong>Chi tit hnh trnh:</strong></p><p>3h sng, mnh bt u t nh  Bnh Tn, thng tin theo i l ng Ty.</p><p>3h30 sng, hm Th Thim vn cha cho php chy. Mnh nh chn ng qua cu Th Thim  n ph Ct Li.</p><p>3h50 sng, ph Ct Li kh vng ngi nn i ph kh lu.</p><p>4h10 sng, sau 20 pht i v qua sng, mnh t chn n huyn Nhn Trch, ng Nai, chnh thc ri khi TP.HCM x b.</p><p>5h sng, mnh r phi vo QL51, thng tin v pha Vng Tu, on ny th do tri ti, vi li cng qu quen thuc ri nn mnh khng dng dc ng chp nh.</p><p>6h10 sng, mnh n cng cho B Ra. Lc  cng bt u i ri, mnh quyt nh lt d bng mt t bnh canh Long Hng ni ting ca thnh ph B Ra.</p><p>6h30, sau khi nn mt t bnh canh tht nc, mnh kim tra xe c, dy rng hnh l ri theo QL55 i v hng Long Hi.</p><p>(C mt s bn ni rng, khi i c hnh, nht l i qua rng ni hay ni vng ngi, m kh nhiu th nn rng  vo yn sau, iu ny c th hn ch vic khch ngi nh xe, hihi. C th c thing, c king c lnh m. Lc i M mnh cng bo nn b ti theo bn ngi, cho chc, h h)</p><p>7h10, mnh n a im chp nh u tin - o Nc Ngt Long Hi - ni cc bn ng ci, y l ln u tin mnh n y, h h.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ACtC-3caSaj-MjB4QrrbtYlQrxhwbZhySXBpZAr5irLnrm9MqqLuHdp0q-OHXjG6roSqDUCr1sK06fwQs8c7TBTjO128FXMdb5BP47uzoS9n57n8Ij5wayQUt9grYGR9kFV0mB105RTON8VHdNfPaVJopSX7=w1150-h1532-no?authuser=1"><figcaption>Hng nng o Nc Ngt.</figcaption></figure><p>7h45, ng thy c mt qun Viva Star, mnh li ang thm c ph nn quyt nh vo lm mt hp, lc ny mnh check bn  th  n a phn huyn Xuyn Mc. Vy l mnh  chy xe gn 5 ting.</p><p>8h10, sau khi ra mt cho tnh to, tnh tin c ph, kim tra cc th, mnh tip tc hnh trnh. on ng ven bin Lc An-Bnh Chu l mt con ng rt p. ng vng, phng, hai bn l c s resort cao cp. Cng c on chy qua rng cy rm rp, rt l th v. Trn on ng ny,  c lc ng h mnh vt qua con s 90Km/H, h h.</p><p>8h40, mnh n trung tm th x La Gi, dng ung ngm nc, kim tra xe c ri i tip.</p><p>Mnh rt tic l t on ny n thnh ph Phan Thit, in thoi mnh gp trc trc nn mt ht nh chp ca on ny, bun :(. Ni thm l QL55 t Bnh Chu n La Gi tng i tt, tuy nhin ng nh, xe ngi dn a phng kh nhiu, li hay c xe my cy, xe ko ghe thng chy chm, nn kh nguy him, d tng t xe trc, cng c nhng on ri rc  g nh, cc bn nn kim tra xe tht k trc khi i v nn chy an ton  on ny.</p><p>9h20, may qu, xe mnh gn ht xng th gp ngay mt cy xng trn ng, may mn hn l cy xng ny c nh v sinh cho khch, h h. Mt s bn chuyn i tour chc cng nh mnh, mnh thng u tin gh vo  nhng cy xng c nh v sinh, tin vic "gii quyt ni bun" lun. Tuy nhin, cc bn lun phi  phng, nn chun b trc xem on ng pha trc c nhiu cy xng hay khng, nu on on trc khng c nhiu cy xng th nn  ngay khi c th, ng la, v nn c thm mt chai xng d phng ct theo hnh l, ng b cp xe, rt nguy him.</p><p>9h25, sau khi y bnh xng xe v x ht bnh trong ngi, :v, mnh tip tc hnh trnh i Phan Thit. Thi tit lc ny bt u nng, m nng bin thng rt gin, oi  nn mnh bt u mt sc t on ny. Tnh mnh rt l, chy xe trong thi tit mt m, hay lnh th khng mt, nhng khi tri bt u nng th c th, u c bt u mt sc, mt tp trung.</p><p>ng DT719 t DT709 n hi ng K G chnh l on ng khoai nht trong hnh trnh. ng kh xu,  g lin tc, ng th nh nhng xe ti i kh nhiu, chc l ch nguyn vt liu cho cc resort gn K G, vt xe rt cc. on ny l on bo sc mnh nhiu nht trong c hnh trnh. Mnh phi vt xe ti lin tc, do xe ti  y chy rt chm, chy pha sau th rt bi.</p><p>9h55, mnh n K G sau hn 10Km ng xu. Qua K G th ng p tr li, ng phng, nhiu dc thoi, cua nh, mt bn l bin, mt bn l hng hoa giy tr bng rt p.</p><p>10h30, mnh dng ngh chn, n nh ti Port c ph ngay cng tu Phan Thit. y l qun quen m mnh hay gh khi n Phan Thit, qun sn vn, rt rng, c view nhn ra cng Phan Thit, l ni mi ngi thng gh khi i tu ra o Ph Qu.</p><p>10h45, sau khi hi t sc lc, mnh tip tc hnh trnh. T y n Phan Rang c hai la chn, mt l ra li QL1A, hai l tip tc cung ven bin, mnh quyt nh i cung ven bin do y cng l mc ch ca mnh.</p><p>11h, mnh ti Mi N, cnh y rt p, mt bn bin, mt bn sa mc ct vng m.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ACtC-3dzOoOrIC1DxVGJNCe_Y6v4jFtsBi-kf-WMXyUir0FQc3vmRVT5QD0pAkIcQVFi0m8Sbpz-OaNR8Kswuf5vHGIdfj6iCGIC11TMbM8uOnHa2Q99PWaRexkqJN9zlvaZs-ciez0_orASFbJXezTF_6-V=w1150-h1532-no?authuser=1"><figcaption>Bin Hn Rm y nng v gi.</figcaption></figure><p>11h20, mnh  ti ng Bu Trng - Phan R Ca huyn thoi. y l mt trong nhng con ng ven bin p nht Vit Nam, l thnh a ca anh em Biker yu thch tc  cng nh nhng bn tr yu thch khm ph. Phi ni l ng rt rt rt p, ng thng, phng, rng. Cm gic nh i gia hoang mc khi hai bn l ct vng, xa xa l ting sng bin. Gi bin  y rt mnh, tt ngang xe nn xe mnh thng phi nghing sang mt bn  gi thng bng. Phi ni l mt tri nghim rt tuyt vi.</p><figure class="image"><img src="http://travel.anandi.vn/uploads/image/giai-tri/bau-hac/cung-phuot-ven-bien-duoc-yeu-thich-o-viet-nam-ivivu-5.jpg" alt="Bu Trng  Cung ng ven bin p nht Vit Nam"><figcaption>Tuyt vi.</figcaption></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://www.chudu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/30590125_2003398123322229_7411729048713297920_n.jpg"><figcaption>p n lc tay li.</figcaption></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://www.chudu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/30829544_157727181732103_981622888694022144_n.jpg"><figcaption>H Bu Trng - vin ngc xanh mt gia sa mc.</figcaption></figure><p>Trn con ng ny, mnh c o th th tc  lc no cng trn 90Km/H. Mnh xin nhc li, ch chy nhanh khi thy  an ton. V y l mt tri nghim m cc bn nn th mt ln trong i, s khng hi tic u, tin mnh i.</p><p>12h, sau khi chinh phc Bu Trng - Phan R Ca, mnh ra khi a phn th trn Phan R Ca. Check bn  th thy l gn ti bin C Thch, hay cn gi l bi  By Mu. Do lc  tri kh nng, nng nn mnh khng gh vo m i tip.</p><p>12h25, mnh ra li QL1A, r phi  i v hng Tuy Phong.</p><p>12h45, mnh  n bin C N thuc a phn tnh Ninh Thun, bin  y rt p, trong xanh.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ACtC-3eR-hZ0Dt3xU40XtT_qc4msFBCfHvAdZzz_AMqB2Tw3MOnNFKqn-Kq8LkZjFpLup1YgBJg1EDhNVIGNfS5QecG6bow783mIuDPOdVULJZOuAYJl863xw3p-iM9aWnwBXvhkWwqxyWfvOHznxpJ-FVIS=w1150-h1532-no?authuser=1"><figcaption>Bin C N, xa xa kia chc l o Khng Hi.</figcaption></figure><p>13h, mnh va r vo ng ven bin Ninh Thun, ti y, cc bn c th i tip theo QL1A, hoc vt o Khng Hi  i mi Dinh. Mnh chn ng i mi Dinh, ti ng ny cng nm trong cung ven bin.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNB1xYcYYiiMYhrmeYlYM6mwoQD08mt3xisR5el=w408-h271-k-no"><figcaption>Rung mui bt ngn ti x Phc Dim.</figcaption></figure><p>13h15, mnh dng ngh chn ti im chp nh o Khng Hi - ng ven bin Ninh Thun. on ng ny rt p, mt bn vch, mt bn vc bin. Nhng cng rt nguy him do o kh quanh co un ln, nhiu khc cua tay o, dc cao trn 10 . i trn on ng ny, cc bn c th d dng bt gp ngi dn dt b i trn ng, dim dn n rung, rt th v.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ACtC-3ekiOSMnL13dJP9Eq_QPMLDzKJtNOUWahbYKrnNoNUk4FNBzfVDdIiayKW1BQSQ72s5hK9yfAxAqlta2MCvUgqU0CrQfeIhqvwioNPm4HuyBjcaC0i74PAF5coj_73uQ2nQQhMQY16Rm9_QTOSDRGis=w1150-h1532-no?authuser=1"><figcaption>Mt gc bin c chp t o Khng Hi.</figcaption></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><figure cla