, mnh n vng xoay Lin Hng, r tri v pha Lin Hng. Men theo DT716  n x Ch Cng v th trn Phan R Ca.</p><p>9h30, mnh vt sa mc Bu Trng n ng ba DT716, r tri, thng tin v thnh ph Phan Thit.</p><p>10h15, mnh dng ngh chn, n ung ti Port c ph Phan Thit.</p><p>11h, tip tc hnh trnh, i La Gi.</p><p>11h45, mnh n ng t Qun Cnh thuc th x La Gi.</p><p>12h45, mnh n a phn tnh B Ra-Vng Tu. Dng ngh mt, ung ming nc, cho tnh ri i tip.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/biVfFjUGxvUD-YRHjNqgb1POsdSlEDg2c7M1P_PyH2SulUfnyaAAsQgndEgTfcTTWAlo1-JbFaL8QqDQrmXtUaLB4TFZqGkrRzq_J7aQnwNIk7MlWqYrOqJTDxqJ5d87SpKjhMMxWN6t9fOEhV6A-OG1asYk0YeMYMkJIIqKNXBHGCmIS5ZSyi-0GhjCbJv2NCKRQ-v4PM5hscRB1uDgQKt6j7Obkh_pWhkI-ANBAp7H9i5fluClQLdg-UPh81OqgmXl8i3YK5a_6NiH2fVHXy8hrJLa9whzPoZfVfVixqjr1TEawDT3fEh1MbIVnRNEBM4SAfKcGyGZEYl0cMVkn7Ql-FalVN4eBoZQgH2X3NvdW1ufJjHPXZa6shM7egGchucZk5rmDSHa3pEHxc-I_GaicEG3cmLO6dJXIEkZVqMcFC0x4KH86LehRVYvf09Uec-dMgfLtKwvYIK7rB8p4xbCy9XhZAeQx6oyjPMSAADqhzDg37Ft-cXi7i4p1fzOpJEtCh55Ah8adFDyU0AEaX9gIxYLyA2AVpYaGP-ikVie9lvmex5i88n5SvnggIZxkqGeZJ6_tYBqudACb7GQb5Jmh1tsMC8cBKSN7yvg0zmeotL8aZ5DugwRk8ddo0p2jwU0PPhZxVACcOn03SgOHs1k2ykmAYxq8tmdaoMZHjg09QOkHy_t61ziyeyc_cjHvCYiuD0cPeqjliMuOBzyzOJlUYMj3IxFR4K96kKnzkWlhsWa5E8FRQ=w1150-h1532-no"><figcaption>7000Km ri.</figcaption></figure><p>13h30, mnh ti cng cho B Ra.</p><p>14h30, mnh ti ng ba Nhn Trch, r tri vo Nhn Trch, thng n ph Ct Li.</p><p>15h15, mnh n ph Ct Li, chnh thc v ti TP.HCM.</p><p>16h ng, mnh v ti nh, kt thc hnh trnh c hnh 1000Km TP.HCM - Phan Rang - TP.HCM.</p><p><strong>Vy l hnh trnh 1000Km c hnh ca mnh  kt thc, chuyn i  li cho mnh nhiu tri nghim tuyt vi.</strong></p><p><strong>Tng kt hnh trnh:</strong></p><p>y l cung xa nht mnh tng i mt mnh, cng l cung xa nht i cng GSXR150.</p><p>- Mnh chn cung ven bin, i qua B Ra, Lagi, K G, Phan Thit, C N, Phan Rang - Thp Chm, Vnh Hy.</p><p>- Tng qung ng c i ln v l gn 1100km.</p><p>- Cung ng c tc  trung bnh cao nht : Cung Bu Trng - Phan R Ca (Bnh Thun), ng rt p, thng, phng, 