hn,  tin trm cho chuyn xuyn Vit,  cn bng li cm xc,  sc li tinh thn,  kch thm ng lc,</strong></p><p><strong>1700Km, 8 tnh thnh, mt cc ca T Quc Vit Nam xinh p. y chnh l tui tr m mnh la chn.</strong></p><p>Chi ph cho 3 ngy 2 m:</p><p>450k xng</p><p>20k v vo Bi Mn x 2</p><p>20k ph ln hi ng trc 7h</p><p>20k v Bi Xp</p><p>6k v cu g ng Cp</p><p>3k ph ct li</p><p>20k v Gnh  a</p><p>47k nc ung ti ch ngh dc ng</p><p>60k nc sui</p><p>150k c ph</p><p>15k bnh canh h</p><p>15k ph</p><p>370k phng 2 m</p><p>50k mua qu lu nim cho c y</p><p>Tng 1.266k</p><p>-----</p><p>Cm n cc bn  theo di ht chuyn c hnh ca mnh.</p><p><a href="https://youtu.be/LfChtcA2fXI"><i>Vlog chuyn i.</i></a></p><p><a href="https://youtu.be/FWJ57bR8_wQ"><i>Mt Ph Yn y cinematic.</i></a></p><p><i>Xem thm cc chuyn i khc ca mnh ti </i><a href="https://dunglu.herokuapp.com/#/blogs"><i>y</i></a><i>.</i></p>', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ACtC-3cN3ufHeiQhkGt5006me6s9JVcakNltQ3x-qGwoAhxxmbKvwHOvxhzARG0SA15LXyOv3aCswW7y4WWlQnhtipfVnvWTpduS-TXKttWLAD4Lssht61b8we5QINX7eaMXVS5H_zMtilue18JBoGAtc-9N=w2724-h1532-no?authuser=1', 1594542224, 1, 1594546428, 1, 1, 0),
	(37, 58, 'Mini trip TPHCM - Mi C Mau | 07/2020 | 876Km trong ngy. Khng!', 'Mt chuyn i thnh cng, mt k lc c lp ra, mt gii hn b ph v. Ngi con ca thnh ph mang tn Bc n vi Cc nam cui tri ca T Quc.', '<p><strong>Eyyo! Xin cho mi ngi, mnh l Qung Dng y. Nhn tiu  chc mi ngi cng l m on ra ri ha. ng ri  (mc d mnh ch bit mi ngi on l g, :v), mnh va c mt chuyn i, phi gi l rt khng, rt in nhng cng rt  v rt t ho, chy xe moto t Si Gn n Mi C mau v v li Si Gn trong ngy. Mnh xin php c k (l, :v) li hnh trnh khng nhng  ca mnh nha.</strong></p><p>Hnh trnh ca mnh bt u t 1h30 sng, mnh phng xe thng theo hng ng ba An Lc v min ty. on ng t Si Gn n Cn Th th khng c g phi ni, qu quen thuc ri, ng tt, rng, c con lng cng gia ng, nhng cng c nhiu on khng c n ng, nn i ti th nn cn thn v gi tc  an ton.</p><p>5h sng, mnh ti bn Ninh Kiu, Tp.Cn Th. Do lc ny tri cn kh ti nn khng thy g ht, mnh ch ngh chn xu ri i tip.</p><p>T Cn Th i C Mau c hai ng, ng th nht l theo QL1A thng ti C Mau, ng th hai l theo QL61, Qun L - Phng Hip ri thng ti C Mau. Mnh th mnh chn hng th hai do gn hn khong 30Km. Nhng mnh s khuyn cc bn nn i theo hng th nht.</p><p>7h, mnh n ng ba vo ng Qun L - Phng Hip, khc vi s mong i cng mnh, ng ny cc k xu,  g lin lc, v cu, rt nhiu cu, min ty th mnh cng hiu, sng nc th phi nhiu cu, nhng cu  y cc k nguy him, m cu rt dc, li nhiu  mi, hu nh cu no cng th, v rt nhiu cu ang trong tnh trng duy tu, nn ch i c 1 lane, c xe ti ngc chiu th phi i, ng th bi, rt bi. Phi ni l chy 50Km ng ny vi mnh nh cc hnh, rt mt, nn mnh mi khuyn mi ngi nn chn chy thng theo QL1A, tuy xa hn nhng ng p, rng, thong hn.</p><p>8h30, mnh n Tp.C Mau sau khi vt hn 50Km ng xu, rt xu, v mnh ngh mnh s khng i li ng Qun L - Phng Hip ny cho n khi n c sa cha ng hong. Mnh dng chn, c ph sng ti C Mau trc khi ra tip QL1A v hng t Mi.</p><p>9h, mnh ri Tp.C Mau, thng theo hng QL1A. QL1A t Tp.C Mau tr i bt u xu, c l do khng c bo dng thng xuyn, do C Mau l thnh ph cui cng trn QL1A ri, nn t C Mau tr i th khng cn  ngha nhiu v mt kinh t nn khng c quan tm.</p><p>10h15, mnh n Tt.Nm Cn, t y, cc bn c hai cch  n Mi C Mau, mt l tip tc chy xe my theo QL1A, hai l i thuyn, ghe ca ngi dn vo, mnh chn cch chy xe, nhng nu cc bn mun c mt tri nghim g  c bit, th nn i thuyn nha.</p><p>11h30, mnh n khu du lch Mi C Mau. QL1A t Nm Cn n Mi C Mua kh tt, do y l khu du lch nn c u t, tuy nhin, vn l c sn cu min ty vi nhng m cu dc v cao, nu i m mi ngi nn cn thn, v ng ny cng khng c n.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ACtC-3dPLrnp7DCDddobPQ0lPhcEimFjX4YWgg0dJAEIXTPm_ecwQeywKt2nmYsdSo8FP1SdzPT4ONYv89eAqoo2baI1i_l2NgMkrblfSG8VNFnskvSwloDnQNvbGwAlXtUvOu4Z_RYuskF4idB84Y1HmXnJ=w1022-h1532-no?authuser=1"><figcaption>Km cui cng ca con ng H Ch Minh huyn thoi.</figcaption></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ACtC-3f63LlF3IbAv254czDGXOp5gfpv-8Bh7BLoBqdKhfsAnCf7akSqxqIFLP63eBtIfEpov-E2of5r8oOOF3T_MgVOtq7Mo64N3pLTITyIsLavzGMNcHT6vy4LoC0RFM-MbKYn1k0QEfMt4XO-HI3ySyGT=w1022-h1532-no?authuser=1"><figcaption>Ct mc cc nam trn t lin - biu tng thing ling ca T Quc.</figcaption></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ACtC-3cKE05Rn-GA_RalFXKUkSkR78HXgZhGHO3d45XTHlNancDrM59WRg80d0RVlXoOihKbfAWrp-hTX7aMzvpsDCWkdB7B8VMX2xWbMULPXUsJHqBzyLKO3jlozWAo57RGkgl49lqIb3mYVBQ1dIIuumA-=w2298-h1532-no?authuser=1"><figcaption>Qung trng ct c H Ni - Mi C Mau.</figcaption></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ACtC-3eHPFutcsrVlnKZLt-OscVe7CRq2NLroTKygMJuH3MZCGsjDWikOY8pbyxHwQgNdSHgVmMwv81qrakfNnfS1Khm88_WyTosOMjRoEDxrGqhCodfkXg_6fEijonaFmYZFjoBNduDqOgTj5kIMZcrDps2=w1022-h1532-no?authuser=1"><figcaption>Biu tng con tu C Mau.</figcaption></figure><p>12h30, mnh ri t Mi, kim tra hnh l mt ln na ri thng tin v li Si Gn, qung ng v d kin l 470Km. Chng v th mnh quyt nh thay i, khng theo l trnh lc i, mnh s i t C Mau theo QL1A v Tp.Bc Liu, ri t Bc Liu theo QL60 ti Sc Trng, ri Tr Vinh, Bn Tre, M Tho v cui cng l TPHCM.</p><p>Chng v ca mnh cng khng c g ni bt, ch l cm ci chy cho kp ti thi.</p><p>22h30, mnh v n ca nh, kt thc ngy chy xe cng nht mnh tng chy, hn 870Km, 10 tnh min ty (Long An, Tin Giang, Vnh Long, Cn Th, Hu Giang, C Mau, Bc Liu, Sc Trng, Tr Vinh, Bn Tre), check-in cc nam T Quc, tt c ch din ra trong vng 21 ting ng h, tht s rt cm xc. Rt tuyt vi.</p><p>Track map chuyn i, mi ngi c th tham kho ti <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/d/edit?mid=1uLnXpgjhoM_X4Zy01xB6f60J9RJeXtrL&amp;usp=sharing">y.</a></p><p>Vlog chuyn i ti <a href="https://youtu.be/iZ4kpbx0gFE">y.</a></p><p><i>Mi ngi cng c th xem thm cc chuyn i Ph Yn xinh p ca mnh ti </i><a href="https://dunglu.herokuapp.com/#/blog/35"><i>y.</i></a></p><p><i>Xem thm nhiu chuyn i khc ti </i><a href="https://dunglu.herokuapp.com/#/blogs"><i>y.</i></a></p>', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ACtC-3cKt2LTBKB8kyyFtmp9FQ973kg6cMnMlw8FIEmSzIr2l1uRyjnishWwUSDViMB-xT3woqonNZYYnflr2hVGkBOvClDlpQHB4V5hM-1C9Yhb8iZFsqd4KP1YPnFKkxBgYQn0O8ATwcqAdNy-1GsKVAkL=w1022-h1532-no?authuser=1', 1595558513, 1, 1607573071, 1, 1, 0);
